    //     1: Stand-Alone PVT
    //     2: Differential PVT
    //     3: Fixed location
    //     4: RTK with fixed ambiguities
    //     5: RTK with float ambiguities
    //     6: SBAS aided PVT
    //     7: moving-base RTK with fixed ambiguities
    //     8: moving-base RTK with float ambiguities
    //     9: Reserved
